    {
      "content": "Engineering a 2D/3D (HOOC(CH2)4NH3)2PbI4/CH3NH3PbI3 perovskite junction creates an exceptional gradually-organized multi-dimensional interface that combines 2D perovskite stability with 3D perovskite charge transport",
